{"tid":1454742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 所有航班已取消 極有可能係想進行圍捕","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:41:07.000Z","uid":30268,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6001a4f96d8184bddbbedea3cba51edbe9f59a17","tid":1454742,"uid":30268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"啱先機管局已經宣佈咗今日淨返嘅所有航班已經取消<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極有可能係想等現場冇哂旅客之後清場圍捕</span></span></span><br />\n已經有手足開post 影到現場有疑似犬隻 肯定又想搞事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家一定要提高警覺</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 我唔係叫人走 唔好屌我"},{"pid":"5299270f6f03f1330a985308272966784628a612","tid":1454742,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有航班已取消!<br />\n機場圍捕無路走！<br />\n所有手足請即散<br />\n記得係一齊散<br />\n唔好落單！<br />\n擇日再戰<br />\n切實執行不被捕原則！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYyt3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYyt3j.png&h=916dd304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMoRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMoRgG.png&h=734c1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBrP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBrP8.png&h=f9aef586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"743892a68412e357fba65c96a8441e0ddbd0f571","tid":1454742,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ece37143c54b4ee519cd6a0a3aceabda6d20f6c","tid":1454742,"uid":286753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78440eadab3cf0184b66cf5190054d5143078c4a","tid":1454742,"uid":288580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748d31ce2e2054719eaaebc04a4c8c91dbe9712f","tid":1454742,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"Be water !!!"},{"pid":"3d72c87a59375feba19347305975853e5e5ffc53","tid":1454742,"uid":198224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"#醒水 #BeSmartWater #你嚟我就散<br />\n<br />\n#機場員工表示<br />\n今晚有機放催淚<br />\n飛機升降 開始 控制 <br />\n6點 只有 起飛 降落 加埋得 40班 <br />\n9點 就 起飛 降落 減到 只得 30班<br />\n警琴晚開始已經不停運gear入去<br />\n警都不停入緊去<br />\n<br />\n#機場Jardine員工一手料*<br />\n老細話Departure 已經封哂，所有人不得進入，有防暴警察入緊黎，老細叫我地走先<br />\n<br />\n已fact checked<br />\nAA sent message to all airline management.<br />\n今天餘下所有航班取消<br />\n已從外站起飛嘅航班有機會未能於香港國際機場降落<br />\n而未起飛嘅亦唔會俾clearance走<br />\n<br />\n係機場既真係要走, 一手資料機場會Close"},{"pid":"47e256833fc55b9c1e0728eb441d4e07ad427ae3","tid":1454742,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"走啦。都叫咗走。"},{"pid":"43650c908ff78c750e4eab51f8e20a80f8fa857a","tid":1454742,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"擺明落閂放狗 快閃啦各位"},{"pid":"67cc4ce036eb1a703a10f8ff287bf7c416c3325e","tid":1454742,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"無人即係無機接，無機接即係非法集會。<br />\n大家走啦，下次再去過啦，危險呀。"},{"pid":"73179a0b7b0617292afde55dc17c2cb8e62e5445","tid":1454742,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"圍捕機會唔大。<br />\n但留係度冇意義，目的已達。<br />\n<br />\n15:50】機管局表示，除已完成航班登機程序的離港航班，以及正前往香港的抵港航班外,其餘今日所有航班已全部取消。<br />\n<br />\n大家盡量讓老弱婦孺先撤"},{"pid":"f21bb5abf3a47cc97a72553bdbd89dd4364d76c8","tid":1454742,"uid":30268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"自推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}